title: Average retail price for regular , unleaded gasoline in Canada 2015 to 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart represents Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 12 Months for 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019.
All through the Months, similar trend was observed for 2016 and 2015. In both cases, the Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter have decreased.
In Month May, 2018 had the highest Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter 1359.0 among the 5 groups and in Feb, 2016 had the lowest Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter 867.0.
Among all the Months, 2016 had the highest Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter in Month Jun and lowest Average retail price in Canadian cents pet liter in Month Feb.
